attributes.Long form description: The student changes the battery and micro sd card for the GoPro before assembling the strap onto the GoPro. The student exchanges the mount from the strap to the tripod before disassembling the tripod on the GoPro and changing it to the handle mount. The student removes the handle mount from the GoPro.

In front of you, you will see a GoPro camera. We'll be using it for the next task.
